P2017090300595.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n#HKFerrisWheel #HarbourFront #Tourism #HKgovt #HK #PaulZ<br />\n#香港摩天輪 #海濱 #旅遊業 #香港政府 #香港 #司馬文</blockquote><br />\n係喎，個野起足三年咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇個野根本唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  三年之後又可以話咩活動收益不如預期，收返塊地起樓。。。l"},{"pid":"1210e4c71a1a7e0ba5dd2b27c2951c052e5fc1f5","tid":386774,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>待用地轉交新營辦商之後，新的三年短期租約會隨即開始。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">若</span></span>新營辦商需安裝新摩天輪，其開始營運摩天輪的時間，將視乎新營辦商取得相關許可和牌照的時間。在進行所需工程和申請牌照期間，新營辦商亦可以在用地內提供輔助設施或舉辦活動，讓公眾盡早享用用地內的設施。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你老母！如果佢可以唔做WHEEL, 咁講乜柒技術標呀！<br />\n<br />\n仆街！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於明司馬文嗰結論點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4026bde055f10c1d2ebf98301d2e6a52e6afe1","tid":386774,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實間野而家係咪可以用塊地做咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算條款真係要有摩天輪佢係咪大可以是但放個aia嘉年華機動嗰種級數既兩三層樓摩天輪仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後主力用塊地嚟做餐飲/商店/其他生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢個tender寫要起55米直徑既摩天輪 <br />\n<br />\n不過 <span style=\"color: red;\">在進行所需工程和申請牌照期間，新營辦商亦可以在用地內提供輔助設施或舉辦活動</span><br />\n<br />\n搞國慶活動呀 國歌演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5684091c9973d2b546b74fd4f0ff80ad3f937e","tid"